ine oil, 點預防flooding, 買車check 壓縮比, warm start cold start, water seal 白煙<br />\n<br />\n有budget 咪買R3 版本不過比得起個舊錢我就唔會買Rx8"},{"pid":"cbed48da2397cca1e095fb8fdc3db81b6f578c87","tid":2200263,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bc4e58ed8ffb43950f662a7851c8a0d8a9e998f","tid":2200263,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T21:38:17.000Z","msg":"Tesla 應該快過rx8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:52:29.000Z","msg":"大把車快過RX-8喎，唔使去到Tesla。<br />\n當年同年份同廠Mazda3 MPS/Mazdaspeed3都係起步快過RX-8"},{"pid":"3c1a98973734fa80bb03c610861b15a9dc189704","tid":2200263,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38878b3b9a7bf12c561a53eef5df8a103eb20b86","tid":2200263,"uid":13556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T23:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁睇唔開買mazda"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:53:27.000Z","msg":"Mazda冇問題，睇邊部"},{"pid":"55bd7e1a8781814d5c26b072e1ff14e62cc4cb9b","tid":2200263,"uid":8060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:45:52.000Z","msg":"香港rx8的保險叫高性能房車<br />\n英國就唔知喇<br />\n<br />\n但係英國玩轉子就一定易過係香港養"},{"pid":"d79260143126635def2042dc16f054eca27abe64","tid":2200263,"uid":293943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:49:35.000Z","msg":"你揸Rx8你"},{"pid":"4fdcd3ee26eb6b7355cc0c3847d77a6cf6ce8872","tid":2200263,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:49:43.000Z","msg":"有錢就買啦 無錢就平平地買部算啦"},{"pid":"4c486c01d716d8e70839552c050e40f9246744a8","tid":2200263,"uid":8060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55bd7e1a8781814d5c26b072e1ff14e62cc4cb9b","tid":2200263,"uid":8060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:45:52.000Z","msg":"香港rx8的保險叫高性能房車<br />\n英國就唔知喇<br />\n<br />\n但係英國玩轉子就一定易過係香港養"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fb1ae19a1af68e69cb29cae33aa783f50496cb","tid":2200263,"uid":8060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:16:48.000Z","msg":"[member]2019年三保唔鎖名，阿牌夠歲0ncb，$3000，第二年折實$2600<br />\n<br />\n1. Daily drive的話，每星期check偈油量及水量，一定要有1L偈油跟車。<br />\n2. RX8比RX7既設計已經比較成熟，唔需要用二沖程偈油/半合成偈油。用普通5w40/30既全合成都可以。<br />\n3. 每次出車都爆一次高轉，以6速TypeS為例，至少上到9000轉響到BB聲。<br />\n4. 裝一隻水溫錶，錶版個水溫計唔準。每次出車都等架車warm up到60度先好踩上3000轉以上。<br />\n5. 買車前check壓縮比, 兩隻缸6個數都有6.5以上就叫正常啲，而同一個缸既3個數值有相差1以上都唔好買，同一個缸啲數字越接近越好。<br />\n6. 諗到再講<br />\n[/member"},{"pid":"c65e146b3f3c08f46d6ceb38a15816499d9665be","tid":2200263,"uid":110353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39fb1ae19a1af68e69cb29cae33aa783f50496cb","tid":2200263,"uid":8060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:16:48.000Z","msg":"[member]2019年三保唔鎖名，阿牌夠歲0ncb，$3000，第二年折實$2600<br />\n<br />\n1. Daily drive的話，每星期check偈油量及水量，一定要有1L偈油跟車。<br />\n2. RX8比RX7既設計已經比較成熟，唔需要用二沖程偈油/半合成偈油。用普通5w40/30既全合成都可以。<br />\n3. 每次出車都爆一次高轉，以6速TypeS為例，至少上到9000轉響到BB聲。<br />\n4. 裝一隻水溫錶，錶版個水溫計唔準。每次出車都等架車warm up到60度先好踩上3000轉以上。<br />\n5. 買車前check壓縮比, 兩隻缸6個數都有6.5以上就叫正常啲，而同一個缸既3個數值有相差1以上都唔好買，同一個缸啲數字越接近越好。<br />\n6. 諗到再講<br />\n[/member"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:38:16.000Z","msg":"How about 火咀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89678dfb3f4ba26b4343e1a8417bd2222f8bed34","tid":2200263,"uid":8060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c65e146b3f3c08f46d6ceb38a15816499d9665be","tid":2200263,"uid":110353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39fb1ae19a1af68e69cb29cae33aa783f50496cb","tid":2200263,"uid":8060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:16:48.000Z","msg":"[member]2019年三保唔鎖名，阿牌夠歲0ncb，$3000，第二年折實$2600<br />\n<br />\n1. Daily drive的話，每星期check偈油量及水量，一定要有1L偈油跟車。<br />\n2. RX8比RX7既設計已經比較成熟，唔需要用二沖程偈油/半合成偈油。用普通5w40/30既全合成都可以。<br /